## Serializers (Blueprinter)

```ruby
class UserBlueprint < Blueprinter::Base
  identifier :id
  fields :email, :name

  field :created_at do |user|
    user.created_at.iso8601
  end

  view :extended do
    fields :phone, :address
  end
end

# Uso:
UserBlueprint.render(user)
UserBlueprint.render(users, view: :extended)
```

