## Solid Queue (jobs)

```ruby
class SendWelcomeEmailJob < ApplicationJob
  queue_as :default

  def perform(user_id)
    user = User.find(user_id)
    UserMailer.welcome(user).deliver_now
  end
end

# config/queue.yml — Solid Queue default em Rails 8
```

